                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen purifying and conveying device and process",
                    "一种氢气净化输送装置及工艺"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a hydrogen purifying and conveying device and relates to the field of hydrogen purifying and conveying, the hydrogen purifying and conveying device comprises a combustion furnace and a purifier, the side face of the combustion furnace is connected with a first gas conveying pipe, the other end of the first gas conveying pipe is connected with a fuel tank, the top of the combustion furnace is connected with a second gas conveying pipe, and the second gas conveying pipe is connected with a flow dividing pipe; the other end of the flow dividing pipe is connected with a fuel tank, a flow dividing assembly used for dividing hydrogen and inputting the hydrogen into the purifier and the fuel tank is arranged at the joint of the second gas conveying pipe and the flow dividing pipe, the fuel tank is connected with a gas inlet pipe, and meanwhile the invention discloses a process for conducting hydrogen purification and transportation through the device. The device has the advantages that the problems that hydrogen-rich feed gas is continuously and stably supplied, only passive stopping can be carried out when the supply downstream fluctuates, and large energy waste is caused by frequent starting and stopping are solved, meanwhile, produced hydrogen can be pretreated, the moisture content is reduced, the load of a purifier is reduced, and the service life is prolonged."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种氢气净化输送装置，涉及氢气净化运输领域，包括燃烧炉和净化器，所述燃烧炉的侧面连接有输气管一，所述输气管一的另一端连接有燃料罐，所述燃烧炉的顶部连接有输气管二，所述输气管二连接有分流管，所述分流管的另一端与燃料罐连接，所述输气管二和分流管的连接处设置有将氢气分流至输入至净化器和燃料罐的分流组件，所述燃料罐连接有进气管，同时公开了使用上述设备进行氢气净化运输的工艺。本发明的优点是，可以解决富氢原料气的持续稳定供应，避免的供应下游出现波动时只能被动停车，频繁的启停造成能源较大浪费的问题，同时可以对产出的氢气进行预处理，减少水分含量，从而减少净化器的负荷，提高使用寿命。"
                }
            ]
